webpackJsonp([0xfa3ea3a004f5],{1050:function(o,a){o.exports={data:{markdownRemark:{html:'<p>I\'ve been using <a href="http://www.alexandrasamuel.com/20050522/make-blogging-part-of-your-workflow/">this tutorial</a> from Alexandra Samuel to set up a workflow that allows you to 1.) post to your blog 2.) post to del.ico.us and 3.) save all your links using <a href="http://www.spurl.com">spurl.com</a>, all at the same time. This, I think will work well for a new biofuels community website that I\'m working on with people in (and around) Piedmount Biofuels here in NC. Pardon any mess I make while I\'m tinkering. </p>',frontmatter:{created_at:"January 26, 2006",path:"/2006/01/26/make-blogging-part-of-your-workflow-otherwise-engaged",title:"1.) post to your blog 2.) post to del.ico.us and 3.) save all your links using spurl.com, all at the same time. This, I think will work well for a new biofuels ...",tags:["blogging","technique"]}}},pathContext:{}}}});
